message.text:
𝐈 𝐖𝐚𝐧𝐭 𝐭𝐨 𝐁𝐞 𝐚 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐍𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞 🤗

Ever wondered what happens when you choose to be more than just a student? Sometimes, the best journeys start with one small step. And this one might just be the sign you’ve been waiting for.

Here in FEU Nursing Society, we’re more than just future nurses—we’re TamNurses who are kindhearted, reliable, and always ready to lift each other up. With every laugh, every event, and every friendship, we’re creating a family worth being part of. And guess what? We’d love for you to join us.

𝐍𝐮𝐫𝐒𝐨𝐜 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐅𝐨𝐫𝐦:
http://bit.ly/3JKoDjY 

𝐒𝐨𝐥𝐢𝐝 𝐍𝐔𝐑th, 𝐠𝐚𝐧𝐲𝐚𝐧 𝐬𝐚 𝐍𝐮𝐫𝐒𝐨𝐜 𝐅𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐲—𝐬𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐥𝐢 𝐤𝐚 𝐧𝐚! 🥰

#NurSocNgarud
#MagniningningAngNursing

Caption by Maria Angela Josephine Aggalut
Publication Material by Rachelle Panganiban

Ever wondered what happens when you choose to be more than just a student? Sometimes, the best journeys start with one small step. And this one might just be the sign you’ve been waiting for.

Here in FEU Nursing Society, we’re more than just future nurses—we’re TamNurses who are kindhearted, reliable, and always ready to lift each other up. With every laugh, every event, and every friendship, we’re creating a family worth being part of. And guess what? We’d love for you to join us.

𝐍𝐮𝐫𝐒𝐨𝐜 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐅𝐨𝐫𝐦:
http://bit.ly/3JKoDjY 

𝐒𝐨𝐥𝐢𝐝 𝐍𝐔𝐑th, 𝐠𝐚𝐧𝐲𝐚𝐧 𝐬𝐚 𝐍𝐮𝐫𝐒𝐨𝐜 𝐅𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐲—𝐬𝐮𝐦𝐚𝐥𝐢 𝐤𝐚 𝐧𝐚! 🥰

#NurSocNgarud
#MagniningningAngNursing

Caption by Maria Angela Josephine Aggalut
Publication Material by Rachelle Panganiban
